Shaul knew how to combine the teacher, the manager, the friend and the team-mate wonderfully, without his various roles interfering with each other.
I want to be as successful as he is in this unique combination.
He raised generations of students, interns and interns, who are now throughout the medical system in Israel, and in their excellent work commemorates his memory and work.
I am honored to be part of this group.
